# Pollux
>The reluctant servant

Pollux was a green and blue [[Dragon|dragon]], bonded to [[Isaak Bondbreaker|Isaak Bondbreaker]]. He had always been a fairly peaceful dragon, often tasked with helping new [[Dragon Rider|Riders]] and their dragons adjust to the [[New Rider Order|Order]]. When his Rider chose to defect to the [[Fallen Riders|King's Riders]], Pollux was resistant and extremely opposed — but ultimately unable to leave his Rider or go against his wishes, especially given the fact that he had already given Isaak his [[Eldunarí|Eldunarí]]. The resulting trauma of being forced into the [[King Pirphal|Sorcerer King]]'s service slowed eroded his sanity. By the time of his death, he had already been driven completely mad. Although it seems that his mind has been slowly healing in his [[Eldunarí|Eldunarí]], for the most part he is silent and closed off from all interaction.
